        <li>Traffic destined for Midtown must exit well to the north or on the far south end of Midtown.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="problem-solution">Potential Solution</div>
    <ul>
        <li>Add a southbound exit to McGowen</li>
    </ul>

        <div>A corresponding entrance ramp to northbound US 59 near Mcgowen is also desirable but appears to be less technically feasible. Northbound traffic will need to take the frontage road north to the Leland Street entrance. </div>
        <div class="itemStatus">July 2015 Preliminary Status: not feasible to add an exit</div>
    <div class="itemStatusText">
